<p>英 /'məʊtɪv/    美 /'moʊtɪv/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.<strong>动机；目的；原因：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Motivation means that you have a good <strong>motive for</strong> action.
